parameters: Maybe I should clean the toilet?
\n<Mister>What will you do? Have a pee sex?
Had pee sex in the toilet...

\n<Eury>...If there's a presence behind us, let's escape
immediately.
\n<Streamer>Hello-con-chin! It's the standard greeting for Tengatsu TV!

\n<Streamer>You know, Tengatsu City is still recovering from monster
damage, and the atmosphere's been pretty gloomy, right?

\n<Streamer>So, I use this streaming room to broadcast fun shows, that's
my job!
\n<Streamer>New girl! Would you like to make a guest appearance?

\n<Streamer>If new girl appears, I bet the concurrent viewers will
increase too!
\n<Eury>But, I've never done anything like streaming before...

\n<Streamer>No worries! I'll lead the way, and besides, you're cute so
you're sure to be popular!
\n<Eury>Cute!? Popular!? Do you really think so~?♪

\n<Eury>(Lifting the spirits of Tengatsu City... for the
reconstruction... Yes, this is part of my mission too!)
\n<Streamer>What do you say? Wanna give it a try?

\n<Streamer>That's the spirit, good on you! Let me know when you can
make an appearance!

\n<Eury>(I thought coming here would be nothing but trouble... but
maybe I've found something unexpectedly fun?)
\n<Streamer>Well then, for today, that's a wrap, otsunpo-tsuntsun♪
\n<Eury>Yes, nice to meet you! Um, what kind of building is this?

\n<Owner>(...She doesn't know, even though she's a sexaroid? Is she
serious?)
\n<Owner>It's a facility where you can have sex with sexaroids.
\n<Owner>(...I see. Maybe it's still not the time for that.)

\n<Owner>Very well. Then, could I ask you to handle the reception for
a while?

\n<Owner>The thing is, people's hearts have become too rough, and
while customers come, there's no one to work.
\n<Owner>I'd prefer if you could also work as a hostess.

\n<Owner>(...A new model sexaroid with emotions. She's a bit hard to
handle.)

\n<Owner>Please come by when you have time. We're always short on
hands here.

\n<Eury>If there's anything you'd like to ask of a modified girl,
please feel free!
\n<Master>Would you like to work at my tavern, if it's okay with you?

\n<Master>I'm sure having a new model girl around would definitely
bring in more customers! Please!

\n<Eury>(Hehe♪ Using the novelty of a new model modified girl to
increase the number of visitors!)

\n<Eury>(It's a bit different from my usual work as a modified girl,
but if my popularity can help liven up the town even a
little, that would be great♪)
\n<Master>Oh, this is great! Then I'm counting on you.

\n<Master>I know you're busy, Eury-chan, so just come and work
whenever you can. It's all good.

\n<Eury>(Working at the tavern... I often get called clumsy by Dr.
Marion, but I wonder if I'll be okay?)
\n<Eury>(...No! I'm not clumsy! Because I am a modified girl!)
